<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:LookupSchemeeligibilityforBSBs-Data&amp;InformationModel=
">Data &amp; Information Model&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"id-03.SD:LookupSchemeeligibilityforBSBs-ParallelAPIRaceConditionI=
ssue:">Parallel API Race Condition Issue:</h2>
<h3 id=3D"id-03.SD:LookupSchemeeligibilityforBSBs-RootCause:">Root Cause:</=
h3>
<p>Multiple asynchronous calls cause earlier responses to arrive after late=
r requests, overrriding correct data with outdated results.</p>
<h3 id=3D"id-03.SD:LookupSchemeeligibilityforBSBs-InterimSolution:">Interim=
 Solution:</h3>
<p>Patch the generated Redux Saga code to use takeLatest instead of takeEve=
ry, ensuing only the final call's response is applied.</p>
<h3 id=3D"id-03.SD:LookupSchemeeligibilityforBSBs-Long-TermConsideration:">=
Long-Term Consideration:</h3>
<p>Discuss with Mesh team to natively support takeLatest in auto-generated =
code for a permanent fix.</p>
